title: Kino (Victor Tsoi) - Ataman
description:
This is an unfinished last album by russian rock band 'Kino', recorded in 2009 and 2012, and abandoned after death of their drummer Georgiy 'Gustav' Gurianov in 2013. This recording contains rare vocal tracks from the frontman of the band, Victor Tsoi (Tsoy), who have died in the car accident in 1990. 

Tracklist:

01. Overture
02. Ataman
03. Bloodtype
04. Star Called Sun
05. Road
06. Boshetunmay
07. With You
08. Question
09. Electrick Train (last mix recorded by Georgiy Gurianov)
10. Kinomechanics
11. Children of Minutes
12. It's Our Time' Our Turn
13. You Have Changed
14. Children Of Minutes (acoustic)
15. Ataman (TV Version, mono mix without keyboards)
